# Enforcement & Anti-patterns (Black-only)

## REQUIRED
- All components use ONLY `var(--*)` tokens.
- Global layout has `<html class="theme-dark">` and includes a single global CSS (e.g., `/styles.css`).

## FORBIDDEN
- Hard-coded colors in markup or component CSS (`#fff`, `rgb(...)`, `hsl(...)`, `linear-gradient(...)`).
- Inline color/gradient styles.
- External libs that force light backgrounds without overrides.

## Overrides
- If a library injects light colors, override under `html.theme-dark` using tokens.
